{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.680", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.080", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.800", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Grundgesetz ist eine Verfassung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.760", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Position bezieht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.440", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die dazu auffordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.680", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Feinden der freiheitlichen demokratischen Grundordnung entschlossen entgegenzutreten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.640", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir in Deutschland haben eine Demokratie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.200", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich wehrt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach Artikel\u00a020 Absatz\u00a04 des Grundgesetzes haben alle Deutschen gegen jeden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.000", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der es unternimmt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.000", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Ordnung zu beseitigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.720", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Recht zum Widerstand, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.480", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn andere Abhilfe nicht m\u00f6glich ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.000", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach Artikel\u00a09 Absatz\u00a02 des Grundgesetzes sind Vereinigungen verboten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.720", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201edie sich gegen die verfassungsm\u00e4\u00dfige Ordnung\u00a0\u2026 richten\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.800", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und nach Artikel\u00a018 des Grundgesetzes gilt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.840", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer die Grundrechte \u201ezum Kampfe gegen die freiheitliche demokratische Grundordnung mi\u00dfbraucht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.640", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verwirkt diese Grundrechte\u201c."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.360", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aus den Erfahrungen der Weimarer Republik und des Nationalsozialismus haben die V\u00e4ter und M\u00fctter des Grundgesetzes den Schluss gezogen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.560", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass eine starke parlamentarisch-demokratische Bundesrepublik selbstverst\u00e4ndlich wider diejenigen vorgehen muss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.400", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die diese demokratische Ordnung zerst\u00f6ren wollen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.280", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich f\u00fcr meinen Teil bin der Meinung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.280", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da\u00df es nicht zum Begriff der Demokratie geh\u00f6rt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.320", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da\u00df sie selber die Voraussetzungen f\u00fcr ihre Beseitigung schafft."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.720", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man m\u00fcsse"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.960", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2026\u00a0auch den Mut zur Intoleranz denen gegen\u00fcber aufbringen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.160", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die Demokratie gebrauchen wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.800", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um sie umzubringen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.040", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So hat es Carlo Schmid 1948 im Parlamentarischen Rat formuliert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.800", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieses Grundverst\u00e4ndnis von einer wehrhaften, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.320", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "streitbaren Demokratie hat das Bundesverfassungsgericht in seinen Entscheidungen zu Parteiverboten schon sehr fr\u00fch weiter konturiert und weiterentwickelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bis heute ist es die gemeinsame Grundlage unseres Verfassungsverst\u00e4ndnisses."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ist aber das Verst\u00e4ndnis \u00fcber die Jahrzehnte der Bundesrepublik gleich geblieben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.400", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so m\u00fcssen sich die Instrumente doch weiterentwickeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.560", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aus der \u00dcberzeugung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.360", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir Feinden unserer gemeinsamen Ordnung niemals das Feld \u00fcberlassen werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.960", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir im letzten Jahr den Artikel\u00a021 Absatz\u00a03 in das Grundgesetz eingef\u00fcgt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.080", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die NPD zu verbieten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.480", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist trotz aller Anstrengungen vor dem Bundesverfassungsgericht nicht gelungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.040", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn zur Wehrhaftigkeit unserer Demokratie geh\u00f6rt auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.400", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie ihre Instrumente unter strenger Kontrolle und Begrenzung\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.480", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei uns durch das Bundesverfassungsgericht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.520", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zur Anwendung bringt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.160", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und so ist es nicht deshalb nicht gelungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.120", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die NPD zu verbieten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.240", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie nicht verfassungsfeindlich w\u00e4re, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.440", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern deshalb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.040", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie im Moment nicht gen\u00fcgend Anh\u00e4ngerinnen und Anh\u00e4nger findet\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.160", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Gl\u00fcck! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.520", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber das k\u00f6nnte sich ja \u00e4ndern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.080", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und deswegen m\u00fcssen wir jetzt handeln."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.680", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit es dazu gar nicht erst kommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.240", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.200", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat das Bundesverfassungsgericht in seiner Entscheidung vom Januar\u00a02017 eine M\u00f6glichkeit aufgezeigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.960", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich anders zu wehren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.000", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Stichwort hei\u00dft: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.520", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Parteienfinanzierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.520", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Deutschland unterst\u00fctzen wir die Parteien mit staatlichem Geld, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.360", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie f\u00fcr unsere demokratische Willensbildung elementar wichtig sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.920", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Parteien sollen nicht von gro\u00dfen Geldgebern alleine abh\u00e4ngig sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.520", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern sie sollen mit der Sicherheit eines gewissen finanziellen Grundstocks ihre politischen \u00dcberzeugungen vertreten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.880", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar das ganze Spektrum ihrer \u00dcberzeugung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.760", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber Geld von der Allgemeinheit f\u00fcr anerkannt verfassungsfeindliche Ziele, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.000", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das darf es nicht mehr geben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.400", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn es gibt keinen Grund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.880", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum wir als Bundesrepublik Parteien finanziell unterst\u00fctzen sollten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.320", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auf die Abschaffung unserer freiheitlichen demokratischen Grundordnung hinarbeiten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.400", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Ausschluss der NPD von der Parteienfinanzierung ist im \u00dcbrigen kein faktisches Verbot der NPD; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.160", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist lediglich eine Sanktionsm\u00f6glichkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.520", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "notwendig als Zeichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.600", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie zwar weiter Politik machen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.000", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nicht mithilfe finanzieller Unterst\u00fctzung durch die Bundesrepublik Deutschland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.320", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch unsere Steuergelder."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.400", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen nicht zulassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.920", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die NPD mit unserer Hilfe die Chance bekommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.000", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wieder gro\u00df zu werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.120", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und damit die M\u00f6glichkeit gewinnen k\u00f6nnte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.160", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "irgendwann doch wieder gegen die freiheitliche demokratische Grundordnung vorzugehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.680", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir beantragen einen Ausschluss f\u00fcr die Dauer von sechs Jahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.880", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die weitere Entwicklung der NPD zu beobachten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.720", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir beschlie\u00dfen dazu heute einen entsprechenden Antrag an das Bundesverfassungsgericht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.600", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lieber Herr Kollege Brandner, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.320", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich sage es noch einmal: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.480", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen dar\u00fcber heute beschlie\u00dfen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "284.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.280", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn wir beschlie\u00dfen einen Antrag und keinen Schriftsatz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.600", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir beschlie\u00dfen heute, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.920", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Weg \u00fcber das Bundesverfassungsgericht zu gehen. "
